//- index.pug
extends layout

block content
  -let source = "https://www.youtube.com/embed?v=9aVJOg2EB9I"
  //- First Section (Blog Launch)
  div(class="main container")
    div(class="row featurette")
      div(class="col-md-6")
        h2(class="featurette-heading") Do you have any artistic recommendations (art, music, design, etc.)?
          span(class="text-muted") I'm so glad you asked that.....
        p(class="homeparagraph") Read what sparks the creative theme behind Bayside Vinyl and its numerous web apps.
      div(class="col-md-6")
         a(href="/posts")
          img(class="featurette-image bvbloglogo img-responsive center-block animated pulse" src="/assets/images/BV logo-2.0.svg" height="200" width="200")
    iframe(width="100%" height="450" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" src=source)
    hr(class="featurette-divider")
  //- Second Section (Other Projects)
  h2(class="bayside-header display-5 pt-4") Explore Bayside Vinyl
  p(class="bayside-header-explanation-2 p-4 lead") Each of the web apps below were created with Ruby on Rails. The pulsating logos serves as link to each respective app.
    br
    //- Second Section (BV Collection)
    div(class="row featurette p-4")
      div(class="col-sm-4")
        include webapps/bvcollection.pug
      br
      //- Second Section (BV Theme Generator)
      div(class="col-sm-4")
        include webapps/bvthemegenerator.pug
      br
      //- Second Section (Official Bayside Vinyl Website)
      div(class="col-sm-4")
        include webapps/bvofficial.pug
      br
